    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it has a minor oil leak and the suspension is beginning to feel a bit loose, suggesting some maintenance will be needed in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price of a newer model.",
