    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This meticulously cared-for vehicle offers the perfect balance of performance and reliability. Having been garage-kept and strictly maintained according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, the exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine with only minor, expected road wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium upholstery has been regularly treated and shows very little wear, while every electronic feature and safety system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. All service records are organized and available for review. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with genuine pride of ownership.",
      "price": 35800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
